\id EZR  
\h Ezra 
\toc1 Ezra Lekhabu 
\toc2 Ezra 
\toc3 Ezra 
\mt1 EZRA  
\mt2 LEKHABU  
\mt3 Ezra Lekhabu Sung Thu Umdan  
\ip Ezra lekhabua kon kimu, vannoi kivaihomna lenpen ahitoh kilhonin, nam mite aki-chon nau thudol aseijin ahi. 539 BC in Babylon lenggam chu Medo-Persia khutnoija anaum in, hichu gamchom’a kon galjam Juda te dingin lungmon umtah anasoh in ahi. Hiche lekhabu hin Juda te gam chom apat akile kit’uva Jerusalem Hou-In asahphat nau thudol jong aseijin, chule vannoi thilsoh jouse chunga thaneipen Pakai ahi, tihi Ezra in aphongdoh e.  
\is1 Ezra Lekhabu Jihpa Chule Ajih Kum  
\ip Mi kimkhat seidan in Ezra in Nehemiah lekhabu jong ajih ahi atiuvin, chule Ezra le Nehemiah jihpa hin 1 & 2 Chronicles jong ajih ahi tin thuchaina asem un ahi.  
\ip Hebrew Bible dungjuijin Ezra le Nehemiah hi akigom khomin ahi. Hichu 440 BC kum’a kijih chai ahi.  
\is1 Thusim Um Dan  
\ip Kipana Thupha! Kum sottah akichou doh nung un Juda ten Cyrus kiti Persia mia kon'in Babylon ana jouvin, chuin Juda te Jerusalem akile uva, Hou-In sah abanjop diuvin phalna apen ahi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Cyrus Lengpa Juda te Asoh Chan Naova konna Kile Kit Dia Phalna Apeh  
\p
\v 1 Persia lengpa Cyrus vaipoh kum masapen chun Pakaiyin Jeremiah kom'a ana phondoh thu chu ana guilhunsah tan ahi. Pakaiyin Cyrus lungthim ana suthouvin alenggam pumpia thuphon khat simphong dingin anathot doh tan ahi. \x + \xo 1:1 \xt Jeremiah 25:11; 29:10\x*  
\v 2 “Persia lengpa Cyrus thupeh chu hiche hi ahi, Pakai van Pathen'in leiset chunga lenggam jousehi keima eipe tan ahi. Aman Judah gamsunga Jerusalem ah ama dinga Hou-In khat tungdoh dingin eingansen ahi. \x + \xo 1:2 \xt Isa 44:28\x*  
\v 3 Mi koi hileh ama mite ho jouse chu Jerusalem’a nache theiyu ahitai, Nangho Jerusalem’a nacheova Pakai Israel Pathen Jerusalem minna nahoupao Pakai Hou-In chu nagasah phat diu ahi. Chule Pathen'in naum piuhen!  
\v 4 Amite ahingdoh tua hingnalai jouse chu hoikom munna khopem hijongleu, akhopem nao gam'a miten sana le dangka a ahin kitopi diu, thilto le gancha jong apehdiu, Jerusalem khopia Pathen Hou-In sahdoh teina dinga deichoma athilto diu kalvalla hijat pichu ahinpeh tha diu ahinalaiye,” ati.  
\v 5 Hijouchun Pathen'in thempu ho leh Leviho lungsung ahin choh thouvin, Judah leh Benjamin phung lamkai ho Jerusalem a acheuva Pakai Hou-In agasapha dingin asol tan ahi.  
\v 6 Aheng akomhon apanhu na in sana le dangka, thil le lo chuleh gancha jong apeuvin chuleh akholjin naova acholam diuvin jong apeuvin ahi. Ama hon acham chamma ahin phaldoh’u chung chon in thil manlutah tahjong tamtah apeuvin ahi.  
\v 7 Lengpa Nebuchadnezzar in Jerusalem Hou-In na anakoi khontheng ho jong chu Cyrus lengpan amaho pathen Hou-In a kon'in ahin ladohtan ahi.  
\v 8 Cyrus in Persia sumchingpa Mithredath chu hiche thilho jouse chu asimtoh a Judah gam'a kilekit ho lamkai pa Sheshbazzar khutna apehlut tan ahi.  
\v 9 Noija ho hi hichea thil kilepeh ho chu ahi:- Sana a kisem kisilna kongho - somthum, dangka a kisem kisilna kong-sangkhat, gimnamtui lhutna lheng- somni le ko  
\v 10 Sana khon-somthum, chuleh dangka kisem khon-jali le somkhat, chuleh adang dang-sangkhat ho chu ahi.  
\v 11 Hicheng chu abonchan sang nga le jail alhing in ahi, sohchang mite Babylon gam'a konna Jerusalem geija ahintol tou chun Sheshbazzar kitipan thilkeo hijatpi hi ahintol tha tan ahi.   
\c 2  
\s1 Sohchanna Akonna Hung Kile Kit Ho  
\p
\v 1 Mihem hijatpi hi gamsung mi sohchanna a konna hung kinungle kit ho chu ahiuvin, amaho hi Babylon lengpa Nebuchadnezzar kitipan sohchang dinga anakai mangho chu ahiuve, abonchauvin amaho hi Judah gamsunga Jerusalem khopi lamma ahung kile uvin ama ama khosung cheh a akile kit tauvin ahi.  
\v 2 Miho chu Zeubbabel leh Jeshua, Nehemiah, Seraiah, Reelaiah, Mordecai, Bilshan, Mispar, Bigvai, Rehum chule Ba’anah lamkai nan ahung kitol uvin ahi. Israel mite amijat mong mong chu;  
\v 3 Parosh chate mihem sangnile jakhat toh som sagi le ni ahiuvin,  
\v 4 Saphatiah chate chu mihem jathum toh som sagi le ni ahiuve.  
\v 5 Arah chate chu jasagi le somsagile nga ahiuve.  
\v 6 Pahath’moab chapa teni Jeshua le Joab chate chu sangni le jaget toh som le ni ahiuvin ahi.  
\v 7 Elam chate chu sangkhat le jani toh som nga le li ahiuve.  
\v 8 Zattu chate chu jako le somli le nga ahiuve  
\v 9 Zaccai chae chu jasagi le somgup alhing uvin ahi.  
\v 10 Bani chate chu jagup le somli le ni ahiuve.  
\v 11 Bebai chate chu jagup le somni le thum ahiuve.  
\v 12 Azgad chate chu sangkhat le ja it oh somni le ni alhing uvin ahi.  
\v 13 Adoni’kam chate chu jagup le somgup le gup ahiuve.  
\v 14 Big’vai chate chu sangni le somnga le gup ahiuve.  
\v 15 Adin chate chu ail le som nga le li ahiuve.  
\v 16 Ater chate chu Hezeki’ah chate chengse ahiuvin, mihem somko le get bou ahiuvin ahi.  
\v 17 Be’zai chate chu jathum le somni le thum ahiuve.  
\v 18 Jorah chate chu jakhat le somle ni ahiuve.  
\v 19 Hashum chate chu jani le somni le thum ahiuve.  
\v 20 Gibbar chate chu somko le nga bou ahiuve.  
\v 21 Bethlehem chate chu jakhat le somni le thum ahiuve.  
\v 22 Neto’phah mite chu somnga le gup ahiuve.  
\v 23 Anathoth mite chu jakhat le somni le get ahiuve.  
\v 24 Beth-azmaveth chate chu somli le ni ahiuve.  
\v 25 Kiriath-jearim chate chu Kephi’rah le Beeroth chate ahiuvin, mihem jasagi le somli le thum alhing uve.  
\v 26 Ramah le Geba chate chu jagup le somni le khat ahiuve.  
\v 27 Micmash mite chu jakhat le somni le ni ma ahiuve.  
\v 28 Bethal mite leh Ai mite chu jani le somni le thum ahiuve.  
\v 29 Nebo gam mite chu somnga le ni ahiuve.  
\v 30 Magbish gam mite chu jakhat le somnga le gup ahiuve.  
\v 31 Elam gam mite jong chu sangkhat le jani toh,somnga le li ahiuve.  
\v 32 Harim gam mite chu jathum le somni ahiuve.  
\v 33 Lod, Hadid le Ono gam mite chu mihem jasagi le somni le nga ahiuve.  
\v 34 Jericho gam mite chu jathum le somli le nga ahiuve.  
\v 35 Sena’ah gam mite chu sangthum le jagup toh somthum alhing uvin ahi.  
\v 36 Thempu ho chu ahile: Jedai’ah insung mite chu Jeshua insungmite abonchauvin mihem jako le somsagi le thum ahiuve.  
\v 37 Immer insung mite chu sangkhat le somnga le ni ahiuve.  
\v 38 Pashhur insung mite chu sangkhat le jani toh, somli le sagi alhing uve.  
\v 39 Harim insung mite chu sangkhat le somle sagi ahiuve.  
\v 40 Levi te sohchanna a konna hung kile chengse chu Jeshua le Kadmi-el (Hodaviah insung mi) chu somsagi le li ahiuve.  
\v 41 Lathem Asaph Insung mite ho chu jakhat le somni le get ahiuve.  
\v 42 Kelkot ngah’ a pang Shallum chate leh Ater chate, Talmon chate, Akkub chate, Hatita chate, chuleh Sho’bai chate abon chaovin jakhat le somthum le ko alhing uvin ahi.  
\v 43 Hou-In lhacha a pangho chu : Ziha chate, Hasu’pha chate, Tabba’oth chate,  
\v 44 Keros chate, Si’aha chate, Padon chate,  
\v 45 Lebanah chate, Hag’abah chate, Akkub chate,  
\v 46 Hagab chate, Shamlai chate, Hanan chate,  
\v 47 Giddel chate, Gahar chate, Re-ai’ah chate,  
\v 48 Rezin chate , Neko’da chate, Gazzam chate,  
\v 49 Uzza chate, Pase’ah chate, Besai chate,  
\v 50 Asnah chate, Meu’nim chate, Nephusim chate,  
\v 51 Bakbuk chate,Haku’pha chate, Harhur chate,  
\v 52 Bazluth chate, Mehi’da chate, Harsha chate,  
\v 53 Barkos chate, Sis’era chate, Temah chate,  
\v 54 Nezi’ah chate chule Hati’pha chate ahiuve  
\v 55 Solomon lhacha a pang ho chilhah ho chu: So’tai chate, Hasso’phereth chate, Peru’da chate,  
\v 56 Ja’alah chate, Darkon chate, Giddel chate,  
\v 57 Shephati’ah chate, Hattil chate, Pokereth-hezzebaim chate chule Ami chate ahiuve  
\v 58 Hou-In lhacha a pang ho le Solomon sohte alhacha chengse chu mi jathumle som ko le ni alhing uvin ahi.  
\v 59 Israel mi hiuvam hilou hiuvam kihetoh jou talou, chulecama hon jong apu apau insung lhah a aki khailhah nau kichen tah a seitheilou ho chu anoiya chengse hi Tel-me’lah a hung kon, Tel-har’shaa konna hung, Kerub a konna hung, Addan a konna hung, chule Immer a konna Judah gam a kile dia hung ahiuve.  
\v 60 Ama ho chu Delai’ah chate, Tobi’ah chate, Neko’da chate ahiuvin, abonin jagup le somnga le ni alhing uve.  
\v 61 Chujongleh thempu thum insung mi akile lah jao ho chu – Habai’ah, Hakkoz chule Barzil’lai ho chu ahiuve. (Barzillai hin Gilead mi Barzillai kitipa chanu ho khat aki chen pi jeh a amin hiche Barzil’laiya konna hi Barzil’lai akisah ahi.)  
\v 62 Mi hijat chun phunggui thusim kijihna ah chun aminu akihol’uvin, ahinlah amin’u akimudoh jou pouvin; hijeh chun amaho hi aboh in akikoiyin thempu ho lah a kon'in aladoh tauve.  
\v 63 Gam vaipo a pang pan jong thilto theng chungnung chu aneh theilou na diuvin ajah uva aseipeh tai, thempu khat’ in Urim le Thummin aman a phun asan masang a aneh theilou diuvin ahil tan ahi. \x + \xo 2:63 \xt Minbu 27:21\x*  
\v 64 Sohchang a hungkile mihem pumpi chu abonchauvin mihem sangsom li le sangni toh, ja thumle som gup alhing uvin ahi;  
\v 65 Hiche hi asohteu pasal numei kisimtha lou lai ahi, asohteu chu sang sagi le ja thum toh, som thumle sagi ahiuvin; alah-uva hin lathem cheh pasal le numei ja ni aumin ahi.  
\v 66 ama hon sakol jasagi le somthum le gup, asakolpol jong ja ni le som li le nga;  
\v 67 Sa-ngong sao jong ja li le som thumle nga, sangan te jong sang gup le ja sagi toh chule som ni, amaho toh kilhon tha dingin akipuijun ahi.  
\v 68 Jerusalem khopia Pakai Hou-In ahung lhun phat’uvin phung sunga upa phabep’in jong Pathen Hou-In chu akisah na mun mama’a sahdoh kittei na din deichom’a thanop’a thilto abol tauvin ahi.  
\v 69 Amaho hin ato jou khamcheh-in natohna dingin, thil kholna insunga atohdoh-uvin ahileh sana daric sang somgup le sangkhat toh, dangka min'a sang-nga alhingin, thempuho kivonna ding ponsil jakhat toh atohdoh un ahi.  
\v 70 Thempuho leh Leviho, chule mipi phabep jong Jerusalem khopi sung dunga aching uvin ahi. Lathemho leh kelkotngah apang ho, Hou-In lhacha ho vang chu ama ama khosung cheh a achenguvin, chuleh Israel mipumpi jong akho akhouva akichen sohkei tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 2:70 \xt 1 Thusimbu 9:2; Nehemiah 11:3\x*   
\c 3  
\s1 Pathen Maicham Athah Tundoh Kit U  
\p
\v 1 Lhasagi ahunglhin toh kilhonin Israel te chu ama ama khopia ahung chenglut tauvin ahi. Hichun Israel mipite jouse chu lungkhat tah in Jerusalem’ah ahung kikhom tauvin ahi.  
\v 2 Hichun Jehozadak chapa Jeshua chu athempu chan khompiho Shealtiel chapa Zerubabel leh a insung mite toh ahung kitho hom uvin, Israel Pathen maicham chu ahin sapha tauvin ahi. Pathen mipa Mose thuhil banga pumgo thilto chu Pakai maichama asem got u ahi. \x + \xo 3:2 \xt Potdohbu 27:1\x*  
\v 3 Israel te chun amun a anacheng saho chu ginna anei vangun maicham chu asempha uvin ahi. Hijou chun ama hon jingkah nilhah in Pakai maicham achun pumgo thilto anabol jengun ahi. \x + \xo 3:3 \xt Minbu 28:1-8\x*  
\v 4 ama hon Lhambuh Kut abollun, hichu Mose daan dungjuiya niseh le anikho a ngaichat dolla pumgo thiltoa kilhaina ding jongchu atoh jengun ahi. \x + \xo 3:4 \xt Minbu 29:12-38\x*  
\v 5 Pakaiyin agonpeh u dungjuijin, angaija pumgo thilto dinga apediu ahin lhathah jousea kibol thilto ding ahin chuleh kumlhum seh a kut ho dingin, ahin tohdoh jiuvin ahi. \x + \xo 3:5 \xt Minbu 28:11—29:39\x*  
\v 6 Lhambuh Kut kipat masang ni somle nga chan nileh thempu hon Pakai kom’ah pumgo thilto a dingin kilhaina anei masa jiuvin ahi. Hiche hi Pakai Hou-In kisah masang’a govam kilhaina chu ana pantauvin ahi.   
\s1 Mipin Hou-In Asah Phat Kit U  
\p
\v 7 Hijouchun mipiten thihkheng them ho leh thingthem bol ho athalah un chuleh Tyre leh Sidon a kon'in thing kitan bongho ahinpo uvin, aman dingin nehle chah lengpitwi le Olive thao anapeuvin ahi. Thingtum ho chu Lebanon molla kon'in ahinpo uvin Mediterannean Twikhanglen pang juijah Joppa geijin akithol lhah sah un ahi. Hiche hi Cyrus lengpa phatsah na noiya abol'u ahi.  
\v 8 Tun Jerusalem ahunglhun jou’u kumni le lhani channa in Pathen Hou-In sah akipan tauvin ahi. Natongho chu sohchanna a konna hung potdoh jouse le Shealtiel chapa Zerubababel chuleh Jehozadak chapa Jeshua leh athempu chanpi hotoh chuleh Levi te kum somni lhing ho leh aval ho chu Pakai Hou-In sahphatna in alamkaijin ana pangun ahi.  
\v 9 Pathen Hou-In sa ho chu Jeshua le achate chule asopi te ho Kadmiel le asopiho chujongleh Hodaviah chilhah ho jouse avesui jin ana pang un ahi. Hiche anatohnaova hin Henadad insung leh evite nana kithopiu vin ahi.  
\v 10 Hiche insaho hin Pakai Hou-In chu aleibul ahin tundoh phat uvin thempu hon avon’u ahin kivon’un sumkon mut dingin amun cheh u ahi kilo uvin ahi. Hiteng chuleh David lengpan anasemtoh bangin Asaph chilhah ten Pakai thangvahna in atumging thei ho ahin suging uvin ahi. \x + \xo 3:10 \xt 1 Thusimbu 25:1\x*  
\v 11 Thangvah pumin Pakai vahchoila ahinsaovin ahi: “Ama hi aphabehseh jenge! Aman Israel te alungset nahi tonsot nading ahi!” atiuve. Hijouchun mipi chun Pakai Hou-In leibul chu ahung kitundoh jeh chun Pakai thangvahna in hasap in asam un ahi. \x + \xo 3:11 \xt 1 Thusimbu 16:34; 2 Thusimbu 5:13; 7:3; Labu 100:5; 106:1; 107:1; 118:1; 136:1; Jeremiah 33:11\x*  
\v 12 Ahinlah thempuhon atehse ho leh Levi te chuleh phung upa dang ho Pakai Hou-In masa ana mukha jouse chu ha kan akap un ahi. Mipi adang ho vang chu kipah tah in hasap’in asam un ahi.  
\v 13 Akipanao husa leh mipi phabep kana ogin chutoh kigom in hatah in ana thongin ahileh gamla tah a umhon jong ajaphauvin ahi.   
\c 4  
\s1 Hou’in Asahphat U Hin Douho  
\p
\v 1 Judah leh Benjamin te melmaten, mikhutna sohchang ho chu ahung kinungle uvin Israel Pathen Pakai Hou-In chu asapha taove tithu ajatauvin ahi.  
\v 2 Hijeh chun Zerubbabel leh lamkai dang ho chu akimu piuvin hiti hin aseijun ahi, “Na Pathen hounao Hou-In chu sakhommu hitin keihon jong houvung kate. Keihon jong Assyria lengpa Esarhaddon in hilaiya hi eihin puilut uva pat’a ama kom'ahi kilhaina kahin bollu ahitai,” atiuve. \x + \xo 4:2 \xt 2 Lengte 17:24-41\x*  
\v 3 Ahinlah Zerubbabel, Jeshua chuleh Israel te lamkai dang hon hiti i nana donbut un ahi, “Nanghon hichea hin chan nanei pouve, chule Persia lengpa Cyrus in eithupeh bang bang uva hiche Israel Pathen Pakai Hou-In hi keihon bou kasahdiu ahi,” atieh tauve.  
\v 4 Hijouchun hiche munna ana chengho chun, Judah mipi te ho chu anatohnauva kichat sah a sah dasah tei dingin anagong’un ahi.  
\v 5 ama hon sumguh in mi ana thalah un, ama hon anatoh ban’u suhboisah din asemdoh taove. Hitobanga amisuhmo gotnao natoh chu Persia lengpa Cyrus vaihop sungsese leh Persia lengpa Darius in laltouna ahinlo chan gei chun anachelha nalaiyin ahi.   
\s1 Xerxes Le Artaxerxes Akonna Douna  
\p
\v 6 Kum phabep jou Xerxes in lengvai ahin hop phat in Juda te melmaten Jerusalem’a Judah mipite dounan lekha ana thotnun ahi.  
\v 7 Khonungin Persia lengpa Artaxerxes vaihom laijin Judah melmaten Bishlam le Mithredath chujongleh Tabeel lamkainan Judah te dounan lengpa Artaxerxes chu Aramaic paovin lekha ana thot’un hichu lengpa dingin ana ledoh peh un ahi.  
\v 8 Gamvaipo Rehum leh Shimshai thutanna'a lekhajih pan Jerusalem’a thil umdan chu lengpa Artaxerxes hetsah dingin lekha ana thot lhonin ahi.  
\v 9 Rehum leh Shimshai chun aloi agolho jouse thalhengin jana lomtah apelhonin ahi. Aloi agol houchu thutan vaihom ho amun'a um lamkaiho chuleh Tarpel, Persian ho, Babylonho, Erech le Susa (hichu Ellam ahi) mipi te ho jouse chu ahiuve.  
\v 10 Chuleh milen leh mithupi Ashurbanipal tin ahin toldoh Samaria gamsung leh avel gamkol sese lhumlam Euphrates vadung geija chengho thalhengin jana kahin peuve atiuve.  
\v 11 Hiche hi alekhathot’u thuchemg ho chu hiche ho hi ahi: “Lengpa Artaxarxes hiche lekhahi nanoija acho chaga dihtah lhumlam Euphrates vadunga chenghoa kon ahi.  
\v 12 “Lengpan nahet louva khoh chu Babylon a konna hung kile Juda te chu Jerusalem munnah achengun hiche khopi phalou tah galbol nomjengho chenna Jerusalem chu asapha tauvin ahi. Ama hon aleibul chu atungdoh tauvin abaang jong ahin jovah diu ahitai.  
\v 13 Chuleh lengpan nahet louva khoh chu hiche khopi hi ahin sahphat kit uva abaang jonghi ahin chaitengu leh hiche Juda te hin nang kom'a apeh dingdollu kai jatchom chomho chu ahin peh nomlou ding nang dinga phaloutah mite hung hidiu ahi.”  
\v 14 “Keiho hi nang khochaga dihtah kahijeh un hitobanga hi min jaloutah a nahin boldiu hi kadeilou jeh uva hiche thu hi nangma jong nahet ding kadei jeh uva hiche lekha kahin thotnu ahi.  
\v 15 Lengpan jong napu napate leng chan laiya thusimbu chu pha tah in kholtoh lechun tumasanga hiche khopi hi gal lungthim pojing mi ahiuve ti namudoh tei ding ahi. Atah bah in hiche khopi hin achunga vaihomte douna a gal anasat jeh uva, hiche khopi hi ana kisubeisa ahidan namudoh ding ahi.  
\v 16 Keihon lengpa nangma kom’a kahin hetsah nom pentah uchu ahileh, ama hon hiche khopihi ahin semphat uva abang jonghi ahin semchai tengu leh lhumlam Euphrates vadung gam kolsunghi nanga konna mangthah tei ding’u ahi.” Atiuvin ahi.  
\v 17 Hichun lengpa Artaxerxas in hiche thu hi ana le thotnin ahi: “Gamvaipo Rehum, thutanna lekha jeh Shimshai chuleh Samaria leh lhumlam Euphrates vadung gamkol sunga chengho jouse salam kahin bol uve.  
\v 18 “Neihin thot u lekhathot chu akiledoh in kahet theidin eikiseipeh in ahi.  
\v 19 Keiman lekha ana kijihlut ho chu kakhol chil sah in ahileh Jerusalem in achunga vaihom ho dounan gal anabol jingui tihi akimudoh in ahi. Tahbeh in amaho hi galbolna hinkho chepi ana hijengun ahi!  
\v 20 Lhumlam Euphrates vadung kol gamsunga chu leng hattah tah noija anaum ma, kai jatchom analahnao ahi ti akimudoh in ahi.  
\v 21 Hijeh chun hiche mite natoh hi angah nadiuvin thu anapetan. Keiman thupeh kicheh tah kahin peh tilouvin hiche khopi chu kisapha theilou ding ahitai.  
\v 22 Hiche thu hi nahsah mon anabol hih in, tu khonung leh lengpa chunga thil phalou ahung umdoh louna dingin chingtheitah in na anatongin,” tin ana lethot in ahi.  
\v 23 Hiche lekhathot hi Artaxerxes lengpa a a konna Rehum leh Shimshai chuleh atoh khompi hokom'ahunglhun phat’in amaho Jerusalem ah alhailut loichal jengun ahi. Hiti chun a thaneinau apodoh un anatoh uchu asutang tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Hou’in Sah Kijomkit  
\p
\v 24 Hiti chun Jerusalem ma Pathen Hou-In dinga nakitong chu atang tan ahi, chuleh Persia lengpa Darius vaipoh akum ni channa ahunglhun tokah sen hiti chun anatang dentan ahi. \x + \xo 4:24 \xt Haggai 1:1; Zechariah 1:1\x*   
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 Hiche phat laitah chun Haggai themgao le Iddo chapa Zechariah themgaovin Jerusalem leh Judah gamsunga Juda te lah a gaothu ana sei lhonin ahi. Amanin achung uva vaihom’ah Israel Pathen min'in gaothu anasei lhonin ahi. \x + \xo 5:1 \xt Haggai 1:1; Zechariah 1:1\x*  
\v 2 Shealtiel chapa Zerubbabel leh Jehozadak chapa Jeshua in amani thusei ajahdoh lhon phat’in Jerusalam Hou-In sahphatna natoh apan lhontan ahileh hiche themgao teni jong chun akithopi lhonin ahi. \x + \xo 5:2 \xt Haggai 1:12; Zechariah 4:6-9\x*  
\v 3 Ahin Euphrates vadung lhumlam gamkaiya gamvai popa Tettanai leh Shethar-bozenai chuleh atoh khompi hocheng chu gangtah in Jerusalem ah ahung’un ajah uva, “Hitia hi Hou-In sahphatna dinga koipen in thu napeh uva, amun jonghi koi thusah a nagon toh uham?” hiti chun thudoh ana neijun ahi  
\v 4 Hiche Hou-In sahna-a kimangchaho chu koikoi ham tin amin u jong adongin ahi.  
\v 5 Ahivangin amaho chu a Pathen un avetsui jing jengu ahijeh in, hiche thudol Darius lengpa henga akiseipeh a chutengleh aman athu umchan dingdol ahinle thot kit tokah in aHou-In sah natoh uchu ana ngadeh pouvin ahi.   
\s1 Tattenai In Darius Lengpa Lekha Athot  
\p
\v 6 Tattenai gamvaipo pa leh Setharbozenai chuleh Euphrates lhumlam gamkaija vaihom a pang jousen Darius lengpa chu hiti hin lekha ana thot un ahi:  
\v 7 “Darius lengpa kajanao salam kahin peuve:  
\v 8 Lengpa nangman nahet tei dia kadei u chu ahile, Judah gamsunga kaga khol’un, loupitah a Pathen Hou-In asahnao mun kagaphah uva thil umdan kamu houhi nahet tei ding ngai kasaove. Hiche kisahphat ah in song phatah a kikheng ho akimangin, apaljong thing apum kikehso ho in akigen pantan ahi. Hiche anatoh uhi ahapan jeh un amachal lheh jengun ahi.  
\v 9 Keihon alamkai hojah a hiche Hou-In hi sahphat nading leh amun gontoh nading’a hi koipen in phalna napeh uham tin kadongun ahi.  
\v 10 Chuleh alamkai hou minjong kahin hetsah theina diuvin kadongun ahi.  
\v 11 ama hon hiti hin eidinbut un ahi, “Keiho hi lei leh van Pathen lhachate kahiuve, chuleh kum tamtah masanga Israel leng lentah khat’in anasahdohsa Hou-In chu keihon asha phat kit u ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 12 Ahinlah kapu kapa teuvin van Pathen chu ana sulunghang’un ahileh aman Babylon lengpa Nebuchadnezzer khutna ana pehdoh uva, aman Hou-In chu asuhset’a amaho chu Babylon a sohchang dingin anakoijin ahi. \x + \xo 5:12 \xt 2 Lengte 25:8-12; 2 Thusimbu 36:17-20; Jeremiah 52:12-15\x*  
\v 13 Ahivangin, Babylon lengpa Cyrus in ama leng chanjou kumkhat sungin hiche Pathen Hou-In hi sahphatna dingin thupeh ana neiyin ahi. \x + \xo 5:13 \xt Ezra 1:2-11\x*  
\v 14 Nebuchadnezzer in Jerusalem a Pathen Hou-In sung’a konna ana lahdoh, sana leh dangka khon, Babylon Hou-In a anakoi ho jong chu ana le lahdoh in ahi. Hiche khon ana la doh ho chu, Cyrus lengpan Judah gam vaipoa ana nganse Sheshbazzar khut’ah ana pelut in ahi.  
\v 15 Lengpan chun hiche khon ho chu Jerusalem a alethah lut kit ding le Pathen Hou-In chu amun mama a chu sahphat kit dingin thu anape in ahi.  
\v 16 Hijeh chun Sheshbazzar chu ahungin Jerusalem ah Pathen Hou-In munchu ahung semtoh tan ahi. Hichea pat achu amipiten ana atoh pat’ u ahitan ahinla anajolou laiyu ahi.  
\v 17 Hijeh chun lengpa lunglam ahi ding leh, Jerusalem a Pathen Hou-In chu sahphatna dinga thupeh umham um louham ti Babylon lengte thusimbu chu kikholchil leh tia ka-nga u ahi. Chujou tengleh lengpan hiche thudolla nalunggel chu neihin hetsah diuva kahin ngeh u ahi,” atiuve.   
\c 6  
\s1 Darius Lengpan Phalna Apeh  
\p
\v 1 Hijeh chun Darius lengpan jong thu apen, Babylon gamsunga lengte thusim kisutlutna a chun akholsah tan ahi.  
\v 2 Hiti chun ahin khol’un ahileh Media gamkol sunga Ecbatana khopia chun lekhajol khat hi amudoh tauvin, hichea chun hiti hin akijih in ahi:  
\v 3 “Cyrus lengpa vaihom kumkhat channa in lengpan thu anapen Jerusalem’a Hou-In chu kilhaina gantha kibol na leh pumgo thilto kitonaji Hou-In chu kithah sahkit hen, a-in sandol chu tong somgup hihenlang availam jong tong somgup ma hihen.  
\v 4 Songtum lentah tah gol thum'in kigol henlantg chuleh thingtum jong golkhat in kigol hen, huting leh hiche songho hileh in-thil ho hijongleh, hiche nakitohna a lut ho jouse chu lengte sumkhol na a konna kimang chading ahi.  
\v 5 Chuleh Jerusalem khopia Pathen Hou-In muntheng phunga konna sana le dangka khonle lheng Nebuchadnezzer in anapoh manga Babylona anakoi ho chu nungpoh lut cheh kitding ana kikoina mun mama a chu koikit ding ahi. Hiche ho jouse chu Pathen Hou-In ah kinung pohlut kitding ahi.” Akitin ahi.  
\v 6 Hijeh chun Darius lengpan hiti hin thu ale thot tan ahi: “Tun hitiding ahi, Euphtates vadung lhumlam gamkaija gamvaipo Tattenai leh Shethar-Bozenai, chuleh Euphrates vadung lhumlam gamkaiya vaipo holah natoh khompi, nangho kikang seuvin!  
\v 7 Pathen'in asah naova chun suboi hihbeh un. Hiche Hou-In chu ana kisah patna mun mama a chu asahphat kit diu ahi. Judah gam vaipopa ahin natoh vaihom Judah upaho ahin sutang hihbeh un.  
\v 8 Hiche chungchon chun hiche pathen Hou-In asah naova hin Judah upaho hi kithopiuvin tia hiche thupeh hi kahin peh nahiuve. Euphrates vadung lhumlam gamkaisea kidongoh kai ho chu hiche ain sahnao manna chu geisang louva napehdoh jengdiu hiche anatoh uhi nasuhboi louhel diu ahi.  
\v 9 Jerusalem’a thempu hon van pathenna atodoh diuva bongchal nou hihen,kelchal hihen kelngoi chal hijongleh angaichat dungjui uva napeh jengdiu ahi. Chuleh niseh leh ama hon angaichat dung jui uva suhlou chang hihen, chule lengpitwi hijongleh olive thao hijongleh angaichat channu chu napeh jengdiu ahi.  
\v 10 Hiteng chuleh ama hon van pathen in asan theidol kilhaina chu tohdoh untin chuleh lengpale achate damtheina le phattheina dinga ahin taopeh diu ahi.  
\v 11 Hiche kadan thupeh hi asuhkeh a aum leh a insunga kon'in alhungpi kibotdoh intin,chutengleh hichea chun ama kikanbeh intin kivoding chuleh ainchu vutvai kisoding ahi.  
\v 12 Hiche Jerusalem khopihi ama min loupina dinga hin lhaang doh Pathen chun hiche thupeh hi palkeh a chuleh hiche Hou-In hi susea aum leh hitobang leng ahilouleh hitobang nam-mi chu kisumang ding ahi. Darius keiman hiche daan hi kasem doh ahin hiche hi mijousen phatah in juisohkeihen,” tin thu ale thotkit tan ahi.   
\s1 Hou’in Kithenso  
\p
\v 13 Euphrates vadung lhumlam gamkaija gamvaipopa leh Shethar-bozenai leh atoh khompi hon gangtah in Darius lengpa thupeh chu ajuipai jengun ahi.  
\v 14 Judah upaho chun atoh uchu ajom jengjun themgao teni Haggai leh Iddo chapa Zechariah thuhil’a kon'in akiha tilkhou lheh jengin ahi. Hou-In chu Israel Pathen'in athupeh dungjui leh Persia lengho Cyrus, Darius, Artaxerxes in daan anasem dungjuijin asachai tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 6:14 \xt Haggai 1:1; \xt Zechariah 1:1\x*  
\v 15 Pathen Hou-In chu Darius lengpa vaihom kum gup channa in Adhar lha nihtum lhinni in achai tauvin ahi.  
\v 16 Pathen Hou-In chu Israel mipite, Thempute, Levi te chuleh asoh channaova konna hung kile hotoh kipa thanopna sangtah pummin alopna asem uvin ahi.  
\v 17 Hiche Pathen Hou-In todohna a hin bongchal jakhat, kelngoichal jani chuleh kelngoi ail akithat in ahi. Chuleh Israel pumpi phung som le ni chonsetna thoidamna dingin kelchal som le ni anatoh doh un ahi.  
\v 18 Hiche jouchun thempu ho leh Leviho chu jatchom chom’in ahom khen’un Mose lekhabua kijih bangin Jerusalem’a Pathen Hou-In’ah Pakai kin abollun ahi.   
\s1 Kalchuh Kut Aman U  
\p
\v 19 Akhovei lha masapen nisom le nili nin sohchang hung kile hon Kalchuh Kut amangun ahi. \x + \xo 6:19 \xt Potdohbu 12:1-20\x*  
\v 20 Hichun thempuho le Levi te chu amaho leh amaho akithenso cheh tauvin athengin aum tauvin ahi. Hichun ama hon sohchang hungkile ho ding leh athempu chanpi hoding chule amaho a dingin Kalchuh Kut manna dingin kelngoi athatnun ahi.  
\v 21 Hiche Kalchuh Kut chu sohchang hung kile kit Israel chate jousen ane uvin, chutengleh thilboh chengsea konna kikangsea Pakai kin bolna a hung kipelut honjong aneovin ahi.  
\v 22 Hiti chun Israel ten nisagi sungin cholsolou Changlhah Kut kipah thanom tah in amangun ahi. Gamsung pumpia chun kipana le thanopna adimlha jengin ahi. Ajeh chu Pakaiyin Assyria lengpa chu amaho khotona aneisah a hijeh achu Israel te Pathen Hou-In sahphatna dinga jong hin Lengpan ana kithopin ahi.   
\c 7  
\s1 Ezra Jerusalem Ahung Lhun  
\p
\v 1 Kum phabep jouvin Persia lengpa Artaxerxes vaihom laijin Ezra kiti khat ana um'in ahi. Ezra chu apa Seraiah ahin, Seraiah pa Hilkiah ahin,  
\v 2 Hilkiah chu Shallum chapa ahin, Shallum chu Zadok chapa ahin, Zadok chu Ahitub chapa ahin,  
\v 3 Ahitup chu Amariah chapa ahin, Amariah chu Azariah chapa ahin, Azariah chu Meraioth chapa ahin,  
\v 4 Meraioth chu Zerahiah chapa ahin, Zerahiah chu Uzzi chapa ahin, Uzzi chu Bukki chapa ahin,  
\v 5 Bukki chu Abishua chapa ahin, Abishua chu Phinehas chapa ahin, Phinehas chu Eleazar chapa ahin, chule Eleazar chu Thempu Chungnung Aaron chapa ahi.  
\v 6 Hiche Ezra kitipa hi Babylon gam'a konna hungtou ahin, ama hi masang laiya Pakai Israel Pathen'in Mose anapehsa daanthu chu kihilla themtah ahi, ama hi Pakai a Pathen'in akithopia akaile jeh'in ipi hijongleh aman angeh chan chu lengpan aphalpeh peh jenga ahi.  
\v 7 Artaxerxes lengpa vaihom kum sagi lhin kum in, Israel chate phabep le thempuho phabep jong, Leviho jong, lathem ho leh kelkot ngah a pang miho jong, chule Hou-In lhacha a pangho jong Jerusalem khopia ahung kitoltou cheh kit uvin ahi.  
\v 8 Ezra chu Persia lengpa Artarxerxes leng chan kal kum sagi lhin kum lha nga nan, Jerusalem khopi ahunglhungtan ahi.  
\v 9 Aman kumthah ni masa niahi Babylon adalhah ahin, lha nga lhin nin Jerusalem ahunglhungtan ahi, ajeh chu Pathen mikhotona khut chun apuijin ahi.  
\v 10 Ezra hin ahinkho lhumkeiya Pakai daanthu chu asim in, amangchan chuleh Israel mipi ho chun hiche daan thu ho leh chonchan thupeh ho jouse chu phatah a anit diu hi atup jing le ahil jingin ahi.   
\s1 Artaxerxes Lengpan Ezra Lekha Athot  
\p
\v 11 Artaxerxes lengpan noiya lekhathot hi thempu lekhathem Pakaiyin Israel te anapeh daan thu ho hoitah a hetna Ezra chu anapen ahi.  
\v 12 Leng jouse lengpa Artaxerxes kitipa keiman Pathen daanthu hethem le lekha thempa Ezra henga kahin seijin kahin lemuve:-  
\v 13 Kalenggam sung’a um Israel mipite leh thempuho chule Levi te ho koi hijongleu chun Jerusalem langa nakile kit thei diuva kaphal peh nahi tauve.  
\v 14 Keimaleh ka thumop the mi sagi hon nakhut uva nachoiju Pathen daanthu dungjuiya nanit soh u hinam ti kholchil dia Judah gamle Jerusalem sung kasol nahiuve.  
\v 15 Keihon nangho hi na Sana ule na dangka u jong nakipoh thei diuvin thaneina kapeuve hiche Jerusalem’a cheng Israel Pathen dia kiphal tah a kapedoh u ahiyenge.  
\v 16 Chujongleh nang hon Babylon gam'a konna nadon doh’u sana le dangka chule Israel mipite leh thempuhon Jerusalem’a Pathen Hou-In na dinga atodoh hou puma nakipoh doh ahi.  
\v 17 Hichea kidongdoh ho chengsehi, nang hon bongchal, kelngoichal, kelngoi chuleh hange mim chohna namanchah diu hichengse chu Jerusalem’a Pathen Hou-In maicham’a nato doh diu ahi.  
\v 18 Hiche sana dangka ho naman val houchu nangho leh na mite chengin, na Pathen'un adeilam tah uva chu namancha theiju ahi.  
\v 19 Ahin khonho vang chu na Pathen henga Hou-In’a manchah dingin Jerusalem a Pathen kom'a h hin pelut sohkeijun tia kanganse nahiuve.  
\v 20 Nanghon na Pathen'u Hou-In na ding ahilouleh chutobang thil danga manchah dinga nangaichat u aum khah tah jongleh leng inpi sumkholna a kon’in kilah jengun.  
\v 21 Keima Artaxerxes lengpan Euphrates vadung lhumlam gamkaija sum chingho kom'a jong hiche thupeh ho kathotnin ahi. Nanghon thempu leh mihilla pang Ezra hin nakom uva angaichat jatjat napeh jengdiu ahi.  
\v 22 Nanghon ama chu dangka pound sang sagi le ja nga chan gei, suhlou chang atena dim ja nga chuleh lengpitwi gallon ja ngai le som nga chujongleh olive thao gallon ja nga le som nga napehdiu chuleh chi adei jatjat jong napeh jengdiu ahi.  
\v 23 Van Pathen'in a Hou-In dinga angaichat ibola eihon lengpale achate chunga Pathen lunghan na ikoulhah diuham?  
\v 24 Hiche to kimat a keiman kathupeh nom kit khat chu ahile, thempu, Levi, Lasa apang ho, Kelkot ngah ho, Hou-Inna lhacha a pang ho chuleh Pathen Hou-In a natong dang ho chu kai jatchom chomho apeh loudiu ahi.  
\v 25 Chuleh Ezra nangmahi na Pathen'in napeh nachihna chu na manchah a Euphrates vadung lhumlam gamkai sunga um mipi ho chunga vaihom ding Pathen daanthu hethemho thutan vaihom ding a napansah ding ahi.  
\v 26 Koi hileh Pathen daanthu nitlou leh lengpa daanthu juilou ho chu gangtah a athu kitanna, kithat ding, ahilouleh kinodoh ding, ahilou jongleh anei agou kilahpeh ding ahilouleh songkul’a kikhum ding ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Ezra In Pathen Athangvah  
\p
\v 27 Hichun Ezra in jong, “Ipu ipateu Pathen chu thangvah in umhen ajeh chu aman lengpa amangchan Jerusalem’a Pakai Hou-In asemhoi tan ahi!  
\v 28 Ama chu thangvah in umhen ajeh chu alungsetna tanglou vin eimusah in, lengpa leh amilen amilal ho masanga eidom sangin hijeh chun keima tilkhouvin kaumin chuleh ka Pathen leh ka Pakai khotona khutchu kachunga aum jingin ahi. Hiti chun keiman Israel mite lamkai ho chu kakou khommin Jerusalem lang’ah kakile tauvin ahi.” ati.   
\c 8  
\s1 Ezra Toh Sohchang’a Hung Kile Ho  
\p
\v 1 Artaxerxes lengpa vaihom sungin Babylon na konna kahin kilhondohpi ho chu insung lamkai ho leh aphunggui’u dungjuijin hiti hi ahi:  
\v 2 Phinehas insunga kon’in Gershom ahin, Ithamar insunga kon’in Daniel ahin, David insunga kon’in Hattush ahi,  
\v 3 Ama hi Shecaniah chilhah ahi. Parosh insunga kon’in Zechariah leh adang ja le som nga akijihlut in,  
\v 4 Pahath Moab a kon’in Serahiah chapa Eliehoenai leh midang jani ahiuve,  
\v 5 Zattu insunga kon’in Jahaziel chapa Shecaniah leh midang jathum ahiuve,  
\v 6 Adin insunga kon’in Jonathan chapa Ebed leh midang somnga ahiuve,  
\v 7 Elam insunga kon’in Athaliah chapa Jeshaiah chuleh adang mi som sagi ahiuve,  
\v 8 Shephatiah insnga kon’in Michael chapa Zebadiah le midang som-get.  
\v 9 Joab insunga kon’in Jehiel chapa Obadiah leh midang jani toh somle get ahiuve.  
\v 10 Bani insunga kon’in Josiphiah chapa Shelomith leh midang jakhat le somgup ahiuve.  
\v 11 Bebai insunga kon’in Bebai chapa Zechariah leh midang somni le get ahiuve.  
\v 12 Azgad insunga kon’in Hakkatan chapa Johanan leh midang jakhat le som khat ahiuve,  
\v 13 Adonikam insunga kon’in khonunga hung Eliphelet, Jeuel, Shemiah leh midang somgup ahiuve,  
\v 14 Bigvai insunga kon’in Uthai, Zaccur leh midang som sagi ahiuve.   
\s1 Ezra In Hou-In A Dia Levi te Aholdoh  
\p
\v 15 Keiman sohchanga konna hungdoh ho chu Ahava canal munnah kakhomin hichea chun nithum kageh un, hichea chun keiman mipi ho toh thempu hichelai mun hunglhung ho chu kakhol in ahileh Levi te khatcha jong ahung pangpoi ti keiman kamudoh in ahi.  
\v 16 Hijeh chun keiman alamkai hou Eliezer, Ariel, Shemiah, Elnathan, Jarib, Nathan, Elnathan, Zechariah leh Meshullam kaga koush in, chuleh Joiarib leh Elnathan jong kakousah in ahi, ajeh chu amani hi thumop them ahi lhon'e.  
\v 17 Chuleh keiman Casiphia mun aum Levi te lamkai Iddo kom'a chun mi kasolin amite a insung mite leh Hou-In lhachaho kom'a chu Jerusalem ma Pathen Hou-In lhacha sunga lhacha a pang ding mi ahinsol diuvin, ngehna nei dingin kasoltai.  
\v 18 Ka Pathen u khotona khut chun eipuihoi jeh un, ama hon Sherebiah kitipa achate le asopite somle get eihin solpeh un ahi. Ama chu Israel chapa Levi chilhah ho lah a Mahli chilhah minasatah khat ahi.  
\v 19 ama hon Merari chilhah holah a kon’in Hashabiah chule Jeshaiah toh ahinsol thauvin chuleh achate le asopite somni jong ahin sollun chuleh  
\v 20 Hou-In lhacha jani le somni jong ahin sol thauvin ahi.  
\v 21 Hichun hichelai Ahava twilam mun’ah hin ka Pathen’u angsung’ah eiho leh keiho kisunem tah a kabon chauva an-ngolla taodingin thupeh kaneiyin ahi. Hiche kataonao chu ahileh, kakholjin naova hi keiho leh kachateu chuleh kathilkeo hotoh eipuihoi nadiuvin kataovun ahi.  
\v 22 Ajeh chu keiman lampi dung’a melmate a konna eihongbit diuva lengpa kom'a sepai leh sakol chungtou sepai thum ding chu jachat um kasan ahi. Ajeh chu keiman lengpa kom'a chun, “Ka Pathen’u hin amahoute chu abanthahat’in ahongbit nin, amavang ama donlouva koite vang alunghanna hoise tah chun asugim jin ahi,” tia kana seidoh tan ahi.  
\v 23 Hijeh chun keihon ka Pathen’un kataonao sana eihoi bitna diuvin an-ngol pummin lunggil tah in kataovun ahileh aman kataonao eisanpeh un ahi.  
\v 24 Keiman thempu lah a kon’in lamkai som le ni Sherebiah leh Hoshabiah chuleh thempu dang som chu kalhengdoh in mopohna panmun kanapen ahi.  
\v 25 Ama ho chun sana, dangka, sana khon ho leh thilkeo dang ho toh lengpa le a athumop them a vaihom hon Pathen Hou-In na koiding’a ahin pehdoh uchu polut ding kapedoh tan ahi.  
\v 26 Keiman hiche thillu ho chu kapeh dohtoh kilhon’in, ka tetoh in ahileh hijat hi alhing in ahi: Dangka ton somni le li, Dangka a kisem thilkeo ho pound sangsagi le ja nga, sana pound sangsagi le ja nga,  
\v 27 sana a kisem khon somni hichu Sana sum pum sangkhat toh aman kibang chuleh sana mantamtah toh kibang sum-eng kilha ngimsella kisem thil ni hicheng hi ahi.  
\v 28 Keiman hiche thempuho kom'a chun: “Nangho leh hiche thilmanlu ho hi Pakaiya dinga athenga kipedoh a nahi taove, hiche dangka le sana ho hi ipu ipateu Pakai Pathen a dinga hung kitodoh ahitai.  
\v 29 Hiche thillu ho hi thempu ho leh Leviho chuleh Israel lamkaiho khut a napehlut tokah un, phatah in chingtup un, ama hon Jerusalem’a Pakai Hou-In'a akoina munna akoi tengu leh phatah a atetoh diu ahi,” ati peh in ahi.  
\v 30 Hiti chun thempuho leh Levi te chun Jerusalem Hou-In'a Pakai thilkoina munna hiche thillu sana le dangka ho chu pohlut nadinga mopohna chu ladingin anom tauvin ahi.  
\v 31 Lha masapen, nisom le ni ni lhin nin, keihon Ahava twilam munchu kadalha tauvin ahi. Chuleh Pathen mikhotona khut chun lamlhon lhungin melma ho leh michomho khutna kon’in eihoidoh sah un ahi.  
\v 32 Hiti chun Jerusalem chu damsel le bit kei chan kaga lhungun hichea chun nithum kakicholdo uvin ahi.  
\v 33 Kagalhun jou’u ani li channa in sana le dangka chuleh adang thillu ho jouse ka Pathen’u Hou-In nah hoitah in katetoh un, Uriah thempupa chapa Meremoth leh Phinehas chapa Eleazer toh Levi mi Jeshua chapa Jozabad chule Binnui chapa Noadiah kom'ah pehlut na le nganse na akinei tan ahi.  
\v 34 Thiljouse chu ajatle agih jatchu aki tetoh sohkeijin hicheng chu agihna jat pumpin kivaipohna dungjuijin hoitah in akijihlut in ahi.  
\v 35 Hijouchun sohchanna a konna hungpotdoh ho cheng chun Israel Pathen’ah pumgo thilto akibolin ahi. Hiti chun ama hon Israel Pathen’ah Israel pumpi dingin bongchal somle ni, kelngoi chal somko le gup leh kelngoi ja sagi le som sagi atodoh un ahi. Ama hon chonset thoidamna dingin kelchal somle ni jong atodoh un ahi. Hiche ho jousehi Pakai kom'a pumgo thilto kin bolnan aneiyun ahi.  
\v 36 Lengpa thupeh chu Euphrates vadung lhumlam gamkaija gamvaipo pa leh vaihom lenpen ho jouse kom'a h akithot lut sohkeijin, hijeh amaho chun akithopi sohkeiyun ahi.   
\c 9  
\s1 Ezra’n Namdangte Kichenlou Ding Asimdoh  
\p
\v 1 Hiche ho jousehi akitoh chaisohkei phat’in Juda lamkai ho chu kakom'ah ahungun, hiti hin asei tauvin ahi: “Israel mipi ho chuleh thempu ho leh Levi te phabep ho jeng jong hiche gamsunga cheng mipi ho a kon'in athongdoh joupouvin ahi. Ama hon Canan mite, Hit mite, Periz mite, Jebus mite, Ammon mite, Moab mite, Egypt mite leh Amor mite chonna kidah umtah ho abol tauvin ahi.  
\v 2 Ajeh chu Israel miten hiche mite numei ho chu akichenpiu vin chuleh amahoa kon hin achate diuvin ji apuipeh un ahi. Hijeh chun hiche kichenna a kilah toh'in namtheng hi asuboh tan ahi. Hiche chungchonna akhoh cheh khat chu lamkai ho leh vaihom ho jengin jong hiche thil dihlou tah kibol hi alamkai tauvin ahi,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 3 Hiche thu hi kajahdoh phat’in, kasangkhol kaponsil kabottel jengin, kalujang’a kon’in kasam katan lhan kabengmul jong kabotchaiyin, lungthim tongkhatah in katou lhajeng tan ahi.  
\v 4 Sohchang’a hung kile hon hitobang thil dihloutah pihi ahin tohdoh jeng phat’un, Israel Pathen thusei kichatna neiho chengchu ahungun, eihung toupi tauvin ahi. Hiti chun keima jong nilhah teng kilhaina phat ahunglhun tokahsen lungthim natah in thipbeh in katou jingin ahi.  
\v 5 Kilhaina phat ahung lhunphat in von kibottel pumleh lungkham puma katouna a kon'in kahung dingdoh jengin, kadilsun ka Pathen langa chun kakhut kadom sangin,  
\v 6 Keima kataovin, “O ka Pathen keima jachat nan kadimtai, namai lang hin ngat ding jong kajah achatai. Ajeh chu kachonset naohi kaluchangu sangin asang jotai chuleh kathepmo naohin van ahin phatai.  
\v 7 Kapu appa teuva pat’in tuni chan geijin hiche chonsetna hin kaki phumlut jengun ahi. Hiche jeh chun keiho kahiuvin, kaleng teu ahin, chuleh kathemputeu ahin hiche gamsunga hou neilou te lengho thaneina a kalhalut ji tauvin ahi. Hitia chu eina thagam jiuva, gal hinga eina mat jiuva, eichom gam jiuva tunia kadin mun bang uva hi jumle jachat thoh'a kaum jitan ahi.  
\v 8 Tuhin phat chomkhat sunghin khotona kachangun, ajeh chu Pakai ka Pathen'un mi phabep khat eihinghoi sah tauvin ahi. Aman hiche muntheng ahin eivengbit’un ahi. Hiti hin Pathen'in eihin mit hadohsah un, kasoh channauva kon hin phat chomkhat hi hailhung jouna eihin musah tauvin ahi.  
\v 9 Ajeh chu keiho sohchang kana hiuvin, ka Pathen'un ami ngailutna akhkonna beichun hiche kasoh channaova konhin eidalha den pouvin ahi. Hiche jeh chun, Persia lengpa chu khotona neitah in kachung’uvah na atohsah in ahi. Aman eihin kiledoh sah un ka Pathen'u Hou-In hi eisem phat sah un, amangthahsa chu eisemphat sah tauvin ahi. Aman Judah leh Jerusalem’ah lung mongin eichensah tauvin ahi,” ati.  
\v 10 Chuleh tun, “Vo ka Pathen'u hichan neiphahsah jouvu nungsang’a hi epi kaseithei nahlai diuham? Ven avelin keihon nathupeh chu kapaidoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 11 Nasohte themgao ho chun gihna thucheng hiti hin eina seipeh un ahi, “Nanghon nachenpha nao gamsung hi, asunga ana cheng hon kidah umtah le thet umtah jeng chonna hoa apumpia ana suhboh sao ahi. Agam hi among langkhatna pat among langkhat geija thenlou na a dimset ahi,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 12 “Achateu chu nachanu teutoh kichensah hih un! Achanu teujong nachapa teu jidingin pui-peh hih un. Hiche gam mite khantouna diuleh alungmon konna diuvin jong tilkhou hih uvin. Nanghon hiche thuhil hi najui uleh nahung hatdoh diu chuleh hiche gam’in ahin sepdoh gapha ho chu naphat chompi diu ahi,” ati \x + \xo 9:12 \xt Potdohbu 34:11-16; Danbu Ni Na 7:1-5\x*  
\v 13 “Tun keiho hi kachonset nau leh kabolkhel naojeh a gotna chang kahiuvin ahi. Ahinlah kachonset jeh uva kachan diuva lom sanga nemjon gotna neipeuvin, ka Pathen'u nangman mi phabep pihi eighing hoijun neihin kiledoh sah kit tauvin ahi.  
\v 14 Ahinlah tujengin jong keihon nathupeh hi kasukeh kit tauvin, kidah umtah a hinkho mang hotoh kichentona kanei tauvin ahi. Ven nalunghan nahin eisuhmang uva khat jengcha jong hinghoi louhella neisuh gam jeng thei diudol ahi.  
\v 15 Oh Israel Pakai Pathen, nang hi mi kitah nahi. Na-angsung’ah kathemmonao pumin kahunglut ui, hiche themmona jeh a hi keiho koimacha jong na angsunga hunglut ngamlou kahiu ahitai,” ati.   
\c 10  
\s1 Mipin Achonset Nao Aphon-U  
\p
\v 1 Hitia hi Ezra in Pathen Hou-In masanglang ngatna tolla amai bohkhup a, kap pum’a chonset phong’a ataopet hin Israel mipi lah a kon’in mihon tamtah pasal, numei chuleh chapangte geijin ahung kikhom’un lung natah in ama toh akapkhom tauvin ahi.  
\v 2 Hichejou chun. Elam chilhah Jehiel chapa Shecaniah chun Ezra kom'a h hitin ahinsei tai, “Eiho hin I-Pathen'u masangah ikitah jou tapouve ajeh chu eihon hou neilou agamsunga cheng numeiho ikichenpi taove. Ahiyeng vang'in Israel te in kinepna aum nalaije.  
\v 3 Tun eihon I-Pathen utoh kitepna khat neiju hitin hichea hou neilou ijiteuhi da-gam jengu hitin achateu pum’in soldoh jengu hite. Keihon nangma le Pathen daanthu nitna neiho thupeh hi jui tao vinge.  
\v 4 Thoudoh inlang namopohna dungjuijin thil ho hi suhtoh na dinga iti chal-lhah dingham neihil tauvin. Keiho hi nangma nungthopna dinga kahiuve hat’inlang hangtah in tong lhatan,” ahung tipeh tan ahi.  
\v 5 Hiti chun Ezra adingdoh in thempu lamkaiho leh Levi te chuleh Israel mipite jousen Shecaniah in ahin seibang chun boldingin kihahselna neiju hite atiuvin. Hiti chun kihahselna chu aneisohkei taove.  
\v 6 Hijouchun Ezra in Pathen Hou-In masang chu adalhan Eliashib chapa Jehohanan kitipa insungdan achun aluttan ahi. Aman hiche mun'ah chun anjong nelou, twijong donlouvin ageh khovah tan ahi. Ama chu sohchang hung kileho kitahlou jeh in alungkham jeng nalaijin ahi.  
\v 7 Hichejou chun Judah leh Jerusalem gam pumpi sungah thuphon khat aphongdoh un sohchang hung kilekit jouse Jerusalem’a hung kikhom dingin thupeh anei tauvin ahi.  
\v 8 Koi hileh nithum sunga hunglhung lou jouse chu, lamkai ho leh upahon gellhuhna aneijuleh amaho chu anei agou hou kichomding ahi tin aki gong’un ahi.  
\v 9 Hiti chun it hum sungin Judah leh Benjamin mipite jouse chu Jerusalem ah ahung kikhom sohkei tauvin ahi. Hiche hi lha ko lhinna, nisom ni, nikho thilsoh ahi, mipi ho jouse chu Pathen Hou-In mai tollhangah atousohkeijun, chule amaho chu athu khoh jehleh gojuh jeh a adap jeh chun akithing thing jengun ahi.  
\v 10 Hijou chun thempupa Ezra chu adingdoh in amaho kom'a chun aseitan ahi. “Nanghon chonset khohtah chu natongdoh tauvin ahi. Hou neilouho numeiho nakichen piuvin Israel chonset nasuh pungbe tauvin ahi.  
\v 11 Hijeh chun tuhin nang hon napu napateu Pakai Pathen kom'a chun na chonset phongun chuleh ama lungdei chu bollun. Hiche gamsung mite leh hounei lou numeiho’a kon’in hungpotdoh un,” atin ahi.  
\v 12 Hijouchun akikhom mipi ho chun O sangtah in asammun hiti hin ahin donbut un ahi, “Adih e, naseichu adih e, keihon nasei bang banga chun kaboldiu ahi!” atiuve.  
\v 13 Hijouchun ama hon aseibe uvin: “Hiche hi nikhat ahilouleh ni ni sunga gahchai jengthei ahipoi ajeh chu hiche chonset khohtah thuahi mi tamtah natkha a ahitai. Tu gojuh laitah hin keiho katousot thei pouve.  
\v 14 Kalamkai ho’uvin keiho jouse thalhengin hiche thu hi hin boltoh taohen. Koihile namdang numei kichenpi jouse chun phat kitep dungjuijin, akhospi sung’a lamkaite le thutanho toh hung kilhon uhen. Chutileh I-Pathen u lunghanna eihoa konna akitol mang ding ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 15 Hiche tohgon chu Ashahel chapa Jonathan leh Tikvah chapa Jahzeiah tenin bou adeimo lhonin chuleh Meshullam leh Levi mi Shabethai in amani chu ajop lhonin adangsen vang aphatsah sohkeijin ahi.  
\v 16 Hitia chu achelhahna dingin hiti hin agong’un ahi. Hichun Ezra in ama insung cheh thalheng dingin lamkai alhengdoh in hiche thalheng ho chu amin cheh in ajihlut in ahi. Lhasom lhinna, ni masapen nin, lamkai ho chu atoukhom’un hiche thu chu phatah in akholtoh pan un ahi.  
\v 17 Akhovei kumthah kipat nikho chun hou neilou numei kichenpi ho jouse chu akholdoh sohkei tauvin ahi.  
\v 18 Hou neilou numei jia kichenpi thempuho chu hichenghi ahiuve: Jehozadak chapa Jeshua leh asopiho insunga kon’in: Maaseiah, Eliezer, Jarib leh Gedaliah ahiuve.  
\v 19 ama hon ajiteu dacheh dingin akitep un chonset thoidam nading kilhaina a dingin kelngoi chalk hat jong atohdoh un ahi.  
\v 20 Immer insunga kon’in: Hanani leh Zebadiah ahiuve.  
\v 21 Harim insunga kon’in: Maaseiah, Elijah, Shemaiah, Jehiel leh Uzziah ahiuve.  
\v 22 Pashhur insunga kon’in: Elioenai, Maaseiah, Ishmael, Nethanel, Jozabad leh Elasah ahiuve.  
\v 23 Levi te lah a konna themmo changho chu: Jozabad, Shimei, Kelalah (Kelita jong akiti), Pethahiah, Judah leh Eliezer ahiuve.  
\v 24 Vahchoi lasathem a pang chu: Eliashib, kelkot ngah apangho lah a themmo changho chu: Shallum, Telem chuleh Uri ahiuve.  
\v 25 Israel mipilah a konna themmo chang ho chu: Parosh insunga kon’in: Ramiah, Izziah, Malkijah, Mijamin, Eleazar, Hashabiah chule Benaiah ahiuve.  
\v 26 Elam insunga kon’in: Mattaniah, Zechariah, Jehiel, Abdi, Jeremoth leh Elijah ahiuve.  
\v 27 Zattu insunga kon’in: Elioenai, Eliashib, Mattaniah, Jeremoth, Zabad leh Aziza ahiuve.  
\v 28 Bebai insunga kon'in: Jeho-ha’nan, Hananiah, Zabbai leh Athlai ahiuve.  
\v 29 Bani insung akon’in: Meshullam, Malluch, Adaiah, Jashub, Sheal leh Jeremoth ahiuve.  
\v 30 Pahath Moab insung akon’in: Adna, Chelal, Benaiah, Maaseiah, Mattaniah, Bezalel, Binnui leh Manasseh ahiuve.  
\v 31 Harim insung akon’in: Eliezer, Isshijah, Malchijah, Shemaiah, Shimeon ahiuve.  
\v 32 Benjamin, Malluch, leh Shemariah ahiuve.  
\v 33 Hashum insung akon’in: Mattenai, Mattattah, Zabad, Eliphelet, Jeremai, Manasseh leh Shimei ahiuve.  
\v 34 Bani insung akon’in: Maadai, Amram, Uel  
\v 35 Benaiah, Bedeiah, Keluhi  
\v 36 Vaniah, Meremoth, Eliashib  
\v 37 Mattaniah, Mattenai, Jaasu ahiuve.  
\v 38 Binnui insung akon’in: Shimei  
\v 39 Shelemiah, Nathan, Adaiah  
\v 40 Machnadebai, Shashai, Sharai  
\v 41 Azarel, Shelemiah, Shemariah  
\v 42 Shallum, Amariah, leh Joseph ahiuve.  
\v 43 Nebo insung akon’in: Jeiel, Mattithiah, Zabad, Zebina, Jaddai, Joel, leh Benaiah ahiuve.  
\v 44 Amaho hin houneilou numei jia akichenpi cheh u-ahin chuleh mi phabep minjong hiche ajiteu hitoh chajong ana neiman’u ahitai.   